 lenses, or widest diameter of visual field subtending an angular distance no greater than 20 degrees. ( do-it, glossary of disability-related terms ) office emails staff directory administration building (adm) room 110 accessible education center san josé state university one washington square san jose, ca 95192-0168 mon: 9 am - 5 pm tues: 9 am - 5 pm wed: 10 am - 5 pm thurs: 9 am - 4 pm fri: 9 am - 4 pm 